Content.Text:
<NAME_MOB_KATERINA>
I came to see what I could buy around here.
There isn't much yet, but I'll keep an eye on this
place.

<NAME_MOB_KATERINA>
Sometimes, you come across a really good buy
in this town.

<NAME_MOB_KATERINA>
I bought something good here today. I'll sell it
back in my hometown and make a nice profit.

<NAME_MOB_KATERINA>
The great thing about this town, for merchants
like me, is that we can find just about anything
we need.

<NAME_MOB_KATERINA>
I hear this town's Guild Master is a woman. I
admire her.

<NAME_MOB_KATERINA>
If you're waiting for things to change, go make
that change happen yourself. Nothing ventured,
nothing gained.
